OL,3,CPrisoner officer smuggled drugs and
OL,4,Cphones into HMP Parc in juice cartons
OL,6,FA prison officer was offered thousands
OL,7,Fof pounds to smuggle drugs and phones
OL,8,Finto a Welsh prison, a court has heard.
OL,10,FJodie Beer, 30, of Llanharry, Rhondda
OL,11,FCynon Taff, was a prison officer in
OL,12,FParc Prison, Bridgend, when she was
OL,13,Fcaught with the drugs in February 2022.
OL,15,FDuring a break she returned to her
OL,16,Fvehicle in the carpark where she was
OL,17,Fstopped by police officers.
