OL,6,FAfter a search, officers seized a zip
OL,7,Flock bag containing light brown powder
OL,8,Fand tubes of white tablets from the
OL,9,Fcentre console of her car.
OL,11,FOn the front passenger seat, they
OL,12,Ffound a plastic bag that contained
OL,13,Flarge cartons labelled as orange
OL,14,Fjuice, which Beer initially claimed
OL,15,Fsomeone had placed there.
OL,17,FShe was arrested and the orange juice
OL,18,Fcartons were found to contain
OL,19,Fcontrolled drugs of class A and C as
OL,20,Fwell as mobile phones and SIM cards.
