OL,3,CPrisoner officer smuggled drugs and
OL,4,Cphones into HMP Parc in juice cartons
OL,6,FA search of her address was conducted
OL,7,Fand almost #4,000 in cash was seized.
OL,8,FAn application will be made in due
OL,9,Fcourse for it to be confiscated under
OL,10,Fthe Proceeds of Crime Act.
OL,12,FBeer was interviewed and stated that
OL,13,Fshe was asked by a prisoner to take
OL,14,Fitems into the prison and told that
OL,15,Fshe would be paid #5,000 to do so.
OL,17,FShe later met an unknown person in a
OL,18,Flayby where she took possession of the
OL,19,Fdrugs, including the orange juice
OL,20,Fcartons that had been pre-packed, as
OL,21,Fwell as an amount of cash.
