OL,6,FBeer was sentenced today at Merthyr
OL,7,FTydfil Crown Court after she pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to three offences of possession
OL,9,Fwith intent to supply and one offence
OL,10,Fof misconduct in public office.
OL,12,FSarah Ingram from the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service said: "What Beer
OL,14,Fdid in arranging to take large amounts
OL,15,Fof controlled drugs into the prison
OL,16,Fwhere she worked was a gross breach of
OL,17,Ftrust.
