OL,3,CPrisoner officer smuggled drugs and
OL,4,Cphones into HMP Parc in juice cartons
OL,6,F"The drugs had been prepped to take
OL,7,Finto the prison and were clearly for
OL,8,Fonward supply. As a prison officer she
OL,9,Fwas in a position of responsibility
OL,10,Fand her behaviour fell far below the
OL,11,Fstandards that are expected.
OL,13,F"The CPS continues to work closely
OL,14,Fwith our law enforcement colleagues,
OL,15,Fin this case the Southern Wales
OL,16,FRegional Organised Crime Unit, in the
OL,17,Fprosecution of offences such as this.
OL,18,FWe have now begun steps to confiscate
OL,19,Fthe proceeds of this crime."
